g/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a match that was high on intensity and physicality but low on quality in front of goal, neither side could find the net in the regulation 90 minutes before El Kaabi netted the winner in the 116th minute.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the game seemingly headed to a penalty shootout, El Kaabi got in front of his marker to bundle in Santiago Hezze's cross but the players and fans had a long, nervous wait for VAR to check for offside before the goal was awarded.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9989845861792762, \"rank\": 0.000932195097794635, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.212119831329455e-24, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result marked a second consecutive defeat in the Europa Conference League final for Fiorentina, who had reached this season's summit clash without losing a single game.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.634549767030824e-36, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0435573178243165e-18, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \